Date: Wed, 10 Sep 2025 18:39:57 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] drm/panel: visionox-rm69299: Don't clear all mode flags
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bsc#1234429
